# shadcn UI

This project uses **shadcn UI** for all UI elements.

## When shadcn is not initialized

If shadcn UI is not set up (no `components.json` with shadcn schema in the app directory, or missing `shadcn` / related deps in `package.json`), run:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

## Adding components

Add new components when needed with:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component>
```

## Consistency

Keep usage consistent with the existing setup in `next-app/components.json`:

- **Aliases**: `@/components`, `@/components/ui`, `@/lib/utils`, `@/lib`, `@/hooks`
- Import UI components from `@/components/ui` and utilities from `@/lib/utils`.
